(Of course, a transformer wouldn't turn out like a human baby. You'd 
probably need a blank protoform or a stolen one. Somehow I bet the 
two halves of the "parental unit's" genes would make the spark. There 
might be more than one way to make a transformer.)


Quickstrike:




Quickstrike glared at Black Arachnia, his optics wide and still to a 
speechless stare. He locked his crimson optics onto hers. She sounded 
pretty serious. 

He slowly snapped out of his stunned stare and blinked. Deep down, he 
was spooked. But the fact of her pregnant may have saved her life. 

He lightly nodded to her and put his cobra hand over her back. He 
looked at Hell Beast's direction.

"What are we gonna do wit' him?" He frowned. "Ah wanna kill 'im."
